headline.print_headline: Lebanon's Hariri Calls for Lawmakers to Elect a President
headline.main: Lebanon's Hariri Calls for Lawmakers to Elect a President

lead_paragraph: Former Prime Minister Saad al-Hariri on Friday called on lawmakers to elect a president after nearly two months of a power vacuum in Lebanon.
